'''热带风暴贝里尔'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Beryl}}）是[[2006年大西洋飓风季|2006年大西洋飓风季]]期间形成的第3场[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]。系统由7月18日的[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]发展而成并总体保持北上趋势，由于外部环境有利而增强，并达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时95公里的最高强度。接下来贝里尔转向东北，因行经海域[[海面温度|水温]]降低而减弱。7月21日，气旋吹袭[[南塔克特|南塔克特岛]]，并在不久后转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。系统残留继续向东北方向移动并经过[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]，最终于7月22日同逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]合并。

贝里尔在[[美国东北部|美国东北部]]海岸沿线产生大浪，但造成的影响很小，也没有造成人员丧生。[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]所受影响仅限于小雨和阵风，没有报道表明当地有受到破坏。[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋省份]]普遍出现中等程度降水和阵风，导致局部地区停电，但出现的破坏也很小。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Beryl 2006 track.png}}
7月16日，有[[冷锋|冷锋]]离开[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]，在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]近海基本停止移动并逐渐瓦解成地面[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Tropical Cyclone Report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL022006_Beryl.pdf | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100616125856/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL022006_Beryl.pdf | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archivedate = 2010-06-16 | date =  }}</ref>，还发展成两片[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]，其中一个的中心位于[[鳕鱼角|鳕鱼角]]东南偏南方向约490公里海域，另一个则在[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）以南约320公里洋面<ref name="two2">{{cite report | author1 = MAINELLI | author2 = BEVEN | year = 2006 | title = July 16, 2006 Tropical Weather Outlook (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。第一股低气压区很快就组织成[[2006年大西洋飓风季#无名热带风暴|热带风暴]]，但在实际操作中未获命名<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = John Beven | year = 2006 | title = Unnamed Tropical Storm Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131106034906/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL022006_Unnamed.pdf | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2013-11-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL022006_Unnamed.pdf | archivedate = 2013-11-06 | date =  }}</ref>，另一片扰动天气则仍然面积广大且杂乱无章<ref name="two3">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 2006 | title = July 17, 2006 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]]}}</ref>。但到了7月18日，系统结构已有改善，发展出层次分明的[[雨带|带状特征]]，在哈特拉斯角[[罗盘方位|东南偏南]]方向约355公里海域获归类为第二号热带低气压<ref name="td2disc1">{{cite web | author = Stewart | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Depression Two Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-26 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al02/al022006.discus.001.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002113923/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al02/al022006.discus.001.shtml }}</ref>。

[[File:Beryl_2006-07-19_1535Z.jpg|right]]东侧的热带风暴贝里尔]]

低气压缓慢向西北偏西方向移动，经过[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]的薄弱环节<ref name="td2disc1" />，并随着对流带渐趋改善而增强成热带风暴贝里尔。气旋存在大部分时间里所处环境的[[风切变|垂直风切变]]都很少，而且有层次分明的上层[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]<ref name="tcr" />。成为热带风暴后不久，贝里尔的下层环流开始暴露出来，其中的深层对流也很有限<ref name="disc3">{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Discussion Three | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002113925/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al02/al022006.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al02/al022006.discus.003.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-26 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>，但到了次日早上，气旋内又重新发展出深层对流<ref name="disc4">{{cite web | author = Pasch | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al02/al022006.discus.004.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002113935/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al02/al022006.discus.004.shtml | accessdate = 2015-10-26 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。受外流继续改善、[[海面温度|海面温度]]较高的双重利好因素影响，贝里尔逐渐增强，于7月20日清晨在北卡罗莱纳州[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]]小镇[[纳格斯黑德_(北卡罗莱纳州)|纳格斯黑德]]（{{lang|en|Nags Head}}）以东约190公里洋面达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]95公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。

贝里尔沿[[中大西洋地区|中大西洋地区]]及[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]海岸平行移动，在最高强度下保持了约18小时<ref name="tcr" />，在此期间[[对流|对流]]中心发展出[[风眼|眼状特征]]<ref name="chc720">{{cite web | author = Bowyer | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Information Statement on July 20, 2006 | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611122955/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20060720175858.Beryl.txt.en | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20060720175858.Beryl.txt.en | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。7月20日晚，风暴因行经海域水温降低而开始减弱，逐渐逼近的中层低压槽产生转向风力，促使气旋加速向东北方向移动，环流中心于7月21日清晨穿越[[南塔克特|南塔克特岛]]<ref name="tcr" />。由于行经洋面水温继续降低，对流也逐渐消亡<ref name="chc721">{{cite web | author = Fogarty and LaFortune | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Information Statement on July 21, 2006 | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | accessdate = 2007-05-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611122959/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20060721115633.Beryl.txt.en | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20060721115633.Beryl.txt.en | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月21日中午12点过后不久，贝里尔在[[鳕鱼角|鳕鱼角]]以东近海转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="tcr" />。数小时后，温带系统[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]西南部，最终于7月22日同[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]上空逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]合并<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
气象机构起初预计贝里尔会掠过[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、北卡罗莱纳州，因此向[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]从北卡罗莱纳州了望岬向北至[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]][[柯里塔克海滩灯塔|柯里塔克海滩灯塔]]之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]。随着气旋表现出朝东北转向的迹象，马萨诸塞州[[巴恩斯特布尔县|巴恩斯特布尔县]]的[[伍兹霍尔|伍兹霍尔]]到[[普利茅斯_(马萨诸塞州)|普利茅斯]]之间地区进入热带风暴观察预警生效状态，生效范围还包括鳕鱼角、南塔克特和[[马萨葡萄园岛|马萨葡萄园岛]]，这时距风暴登岸还有约33小时。约11小时后，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]将之前发布的热带风暴观察预警升级成热带风暴警告，又对伍兹霍尔向西至[[纽哈芬市|纽哈芬市]]之间地区和[[长岛_(纽约州)|长岛]]东部的[[法尔岛|法尔岛]]到[[杰斐逊港|杰斐逊港]]之间地区发布热带风暴观察预警。<ref name="tcr" />面对气旋的威胁，马萨诸塞州紧急事务管理局进入飓风季试运行状态。当地[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]分会保持开放<ref name="bg721">{{cite news | author = Carolyn Johnson and Yuxing Zheng | title = Tropical Storm Beryl sweeps into region | publisher = Boston Globe | accessdate = 2007-05-22 | url = http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2006/07/21/tropical_storm_beryl_sweeps_into_region/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150603142721/http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2006/07/21/tropical_storm_beryl_sweeps_into_region/ | date = 2006-07-21 | archivedate = 2015-06-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，还有两支志愿者队伍待命，随时准备提供协助<ref>{{cite news | author = Paul Shipman | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Threatens New England with Wind, Rain | publisher = Charter Oak Chapter of the American Red Cross}}</ref>。马萨诸塞州东南部各地警局加派警力，为风暴期间可能出现的问题做准备。许多渔民将船只固定，还有一些商户店主将窗口封死，以免因风暴受损。<ref name="bg721" />

贝里尔经过加拿大大西洋省份数天前，[[加拿大飓风中心|加拿大飓风中心]]就向新斯科舍和纽芬兰岛沿海水域发布烈风警告<ref name="chc720" />，还向新斯科舍西部包括[[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]在内的地区发布暴雨警告<ref name="chc721" />。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Beryl_Jetty_Surf.jpg|225px]]海域产生的海浪]]
风暴在美国东岸沿线产生大浪，开放海域浪高达5.97米<ref name="local" />。气旋逼近期间，南塔克特岛南岸沿线有3米高的大浪<ref name="nasa">{{cite web | author = NASA/GOES Project Office | year = 2006 | title = Beryl's Effect on Nantucket Island, Mass | url = http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2006/h2006_beryl.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150926221718/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2006/h2006_beryl.html | accessdate = 2015-10-26 | archivedate = 2015-09-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，致使4人被[[离岸流|离岸流]]所困，之后幸得救生员救出<ref name="bg721" />。马萨诸塞州南向海岸同样出现大浪，导致[[波士顿|波士顿]]同南塔克特间的轮渡暂停运营<ref name="local">{{cite news | author1 = Andrew Ryan | author2 = Yuxing Zheng | author3 = Peter Schworm | newspaper = Boston Globe | date = 2006-07-21 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl fizzles as it passes over Nantucket | url = http://www.boston.com/news/globe/city_region/breaking_news/2006/07/tropical_storm_2.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120925190552/http://www.boston.com/news/globe/city_region/breaking_news/2006/07/tropical_storm_2.html | accessdate = 2012-09-25 | archivedate = 2012-09-25 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。贝里克在南塔克特产生0.27米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，马萨诸塞州东南部的风力相对较小，持续风速没有达到热带风暴强度，最高阵风时速为71公里，非正式纪录中的最高阵风时速则有82公里<ref name="tcr" />。气旋还在近海产生中等程度降水<ref name="usatoday">{{cite news |author=Associated Press |title=Tropical Storm Beryl skirts Massachusetts |accessdate=2013-02-05 |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2006-07-21-storm-beryl_x.htm |work=USA Today |date=2006-07-21 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130205164004/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2006-07-21-storm-beryl_x.htm |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-02-05 }}</ref>，美国本土的最高降雨量出现在南塔克特，只有24.6毫米<ref name="WPCMAX">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M. | date = 2015-04-30 | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Point Maxima | accessdate = 2015-10-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151022203526/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | chapter-url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | archivedate = 2015-10-22 }}</ref>。马萨诸塞州东南部的降水以[[巴恩斯特布尔县|巴恩斯特布尔县]][[查塔姆_(马萨诸塞州)|查塔姆]]（{{lang|en|Chatham}}）最高，但也只有8.38毫米<ref name="tcr" />。据报道，整场风暴造成的破坏仅限于部分电线杆倒塌和树枝断裂<ref name="boston">{{cite news | author = Boston Globe | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Pays Nantucket a Visit | accessdate = 2015-10-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141213211316/http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2006/07/22/tropical_storm_beryl_pays_nantucket_a_visit/ | work = The Boston Globe | date = 2006-07-22 | archivedate = 2014-12-13 | url = http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2006/07/22/tropical_storm_beryl_pays_nantucket_a_visit/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋的整体影响很小，没有出现停电<ref name="nasa" />和人员伤亡<ref name="tcr" />，也没有在海上引发紧急事件<ref name="usatoday" />。

贝里尔的残留在加拿大大西洋省份产生中等程度降水，正式公布的数据中降雨量最高的是新斯科舍[[金斯县_(新斯科舍省)|金斯县]]的[[苏格兰湾_(新斯科舍)|苏格兰湾]]（{{lang|en|Scots Bay}}），为71毫米<ref name="winnepegfreepress">{{cite web | author = Canadian Press | year = 2006 | title = Post-tropical storm Beryl leaves Atlantic Canada after dumping pouring rain | accessdate = 2007-09-27 | url = http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/breakingnews/canada/story/3604925p-4167132c.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927194114/http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/breakingnews/canada/story/3604925p-4167132c.html | archivedate = 2007-09-27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，非正式纪录中略高，达到88毫米，局部地区在1小时里就降下25毫米雨量<ref name="chc">{{cite web | author = Canadian Hurricane Centre | year = 2007 | title = 2006 Atlantic Hurricane Season Review | accessdate = 2007-05-24 | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/storm06.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070726014055/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/storm06.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2007-07-26 }}</ref>。此外，[[新不伦瑞克|新不伦瑞克]][[弗雷德里克顿|弗雷德里克顿]]的一间气象站在2小时内就测得45毫米雨量<ref name="chc721b">{{cite web | author = LaFortune and Bowyer | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Intermediate Information Bulletin on July 21 | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611123008/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20060721150644.Beryl.txt.en | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20060721150644.Beryl.txt.en | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-06-11 }}</ref>。降雨引发轻度洪灾，部分水道泛滥，淹没了一些街道。气旋沿途出现中等强度风力，其中最高风速出现在新斯科舍北部，达到每小时96公里。大风刮断了一些树枝，还导致部分地区停电，但总体破坏程度很轻。<ref name="chc" />

